divs: Sighting DetailsThe other was shaped like a disk a cloud like appearance around it, I counted not all but at least about 3-4 lights. it was going around and around. it started out with the first shorter description as I described moving in a west direction sitting there for about 30 seconds then it began to proceed in the west direction of tremont avenue going towards central avenue. The craft did not have no sound at all. It was very quiet gliding across the sky. I just woke up exactly at 4:00 a.m. getting up out of my bed looking out my window when I spotted the craft. This is no joke. For a person who didnt believe that UFO's existed, I jumped out of my skin. I knew definitely it was not an airplane, nor jet. ABSOLUTELY!!! POSITIVELY!!! You may call me. But I don't have a camera available, now I will purchase one soon. For sure...
